These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, balloon-flower, daffodil
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, eggplant, cauliflower, kiwi
1. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
2. the person who growsiris is not the person eating strawberry##6
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
6. the person eating strawberry is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | iris   | daffodil    | marigold    | balloon-flower |
| Sport      | kiwi | strawberry | cauliflower | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, golf, cricket, skiing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, september, march, july
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
4. the person who's sport is golf is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | golf  | cricket    | sailing | skiing    |
| Food       | july | september | march  | june |

