.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid, sunflower, rose
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, pall-mall, fonseca, tiparillo
1. the person who growsrose is not the baccarat-smoker##6
2. the pall-mall-smoker is not the person who growssunflower##6
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
4. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | rose       | orchid  | daffodil  | sunflower |
| Job        | fonseca | tiparillo | pall-mall | baccarat  |

