.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, nurse, teacher, videographer
House: colonial, modern, farmhouse, cape-cod
1. the teacher is on the left of the videographer##1
2. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
3. the cape-cod house is not the nurse##6
4. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the colonial house##5
5. the farmhouse house is on the right of the modern house##1
6. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | nurse | teacher | videographer     | scientist |
| Transport   | modern     | farmhouse    | colonial | cape-cod    |

