.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
City: miami, liverpool, new-york, nizza
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, biathlon, cricket, parkour
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
3. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
4. the person traveling to liverpool is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
5. the person who's sport is climbing is not the person traveling to miami##6
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | miami        | nizza | new-york | liverpool |
| Transport   | parkour | climbing | biathlon     | cricket   |

