.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, accountant, mechanic, writer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, rowing, baseball
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the writer is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
5. the mechanic is the mechanic##1
6. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
7. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
8. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
9. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | accountant | mechanic    | dancer  | writer   |
| Nationality   | rowing  | baseball | skateboarding | weightlifting |

