.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, bike, ship
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, surfing, rowing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person driving the motorbike##6
3. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | ship | motorbike     | bike | airplane |
| Music-Genre   | surfing | biathlon | rowing      | cycling         |

