2. the siglo-smoker is not the person eating zucchini##6
3. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5
4. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
6. the bolivar-smoker is the person eating nectarine##1
7. the person eating pear is not the bolivar-smoker##6
8. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | pear  | nectarine | zucchini    | lemon |
| Transport   | siglo | bolivar | aristoff | davidoff  |

