House: farmhouse, modern, cottage, ranch-style
1. the farmhouse house is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing chess##1
3. the ranch-style house is the ranch-style house##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the person playing canasta is not the ranch-style house##6
6. the modern house is not the person playing chess##6
7. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
8. the person playing canasta is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | canasta | mah-jongg        | backgammon  | chess     |
| Sport   | farmhouse     | ranch-style | modern | cottage |

