4. the person who growsdaffodil is between the spanish and the person who growsbegonia##2
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the dutch is between the russian and the person who growsamaryllis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
