4. the nurse is not the person playing backgammon##6
5. the person playing billiard is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing bridge##2
6. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
