.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, freelancer, nurse, architect
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, august, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
2. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is not the teacher##6
5. the architect is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
6. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | teacher | freelancer | architect      | nurse   |
| Transport   | april  | february   | august | september |

 